{"tid":402902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然覺得生命真係脆弱到不得了","createTime":"2017-09-16T18:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T19:21:33.000Z","uid":57476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d371c281f9147e531eba612ffbc6121c20cf65","tid":402902,"uid":57476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/021555_591cd9942c9411818fe3fac710b856da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F021555_591cd9942c9411818fe3fac710b856da.jpg&h=66cc0687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前兩日西貢係自己屋企附近有外國人意外浸死<br />\n又消防又救護車又一車車記者<br />\n已經覺得好可惜話曬一個生命呀<br />\n今日又死左兩個 <br />\n老母成日話該死唔洗病<br />\n真係好撚驚下個就係自己唔撚想死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c14a6788b55dc99af775f1f28ec15f567baf283","tid":402902,"uid":70425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T19:21:33.000Z","msg":"其實係 珍惜眼前人"}]}